summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6261 for the improvement of the alley in Block 101, D.T. Denny's 5th Addition to North Seattle, being the alley between Terry Ave. North and Boren Ave. North from Thomas Street to Harrison Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 90932, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
